---
title: Honey Soy Chicken & Garlic Rice with Charred Corn Slaw & Crispy Shallots
description: Tonight’s dinner takes chicken and rice to new levels. As if the honey soy chicken wasn’t delicious enough, serving it alongside
garlic rice adds another flavour punch! The addition of creamy slaw and crispy shallots add the perfect amount of freshness and
crunch to this irresistible dish.
